WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.133 --> 00:00:02.333
Sister Meng, if Shen Guiying leaves

2
00:00:02.333 --> 00:00:03.666
You will regret it for the rest of your life

3
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:05.600
What is Fu Chuan doing?

4
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:09.066
Get out of the way, he's your biological mother you've been looking for for 20 years

5
00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:11.200
I will never let you drive him away

6
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:13.366
Otherwise you will make a big mistake

7
00:00:16.166 --> 00:00:17.800
I'm Meng Jie's mother

8
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:20.933
He pretended to be me and wanted to seize the Zhang family's property

9
00:00:20.933 --> 00:00:23.300
Daughter, don't be deceived by them

10
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.233
That's enough!

11
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:29.900
Bucheon

12
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:32.600
I believe in you so much

13
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:35.566
You are for the property of the Zhang family

14
00:00:35.866 --> 00:00:38.033
Don't try to kill me with an outsider

15
00:00:41.933 --> 00:00:44.233
I'm so disappointed in you.

16
00:00:45.766 --> 00:00:48.166
You will leave the Zhang family immediately with the turtle

17
00:00:48.766 --> 00:00:51.366
I'll send you the divorce settlement

18
00:00:51.766 --> 00:00:53.900
What? You want to divorce me?

19
00:00:55.566 --> 00:00:57.200
If Bucheon leaves

20
00:00:57.300 --> 00:01:00.033
There is no one around his daughter to help him anymore

21
00:01:11.466 --> 00:01:12.766
You can't leave.

22
00:01:12.966 --> 00:01:14.900
Bucheon did nothing wrong

23
00:01:15.066 --> 00:01:16.866
He is sincere to you

24
00:01:16.966 --> 00:01:20.033
It's all photography as a means of sowing discord

25
00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:21.766
You can't believe it!

26
00:01:21.766 --> 00:01:23.400
He will kill you

27
00:01:25.366 --> 00:01:26.433
Shen Guiying

28
00:01:27.366 --> 00:01:28.166
cool

